
Save all files to a folder called Robot in you're Arduino sketch folder.

Open Robot.ino and the other files will appear as tabs in the Arduino IDE.


This code uses the following library's....

VarSpeedServo.h  // Variable speed servo library by Korman, https://forum.arduino.cc/index.php?topic=61586.0
PS2X_lib.h       // PS2X Library by Bill Porter, http://www.billporter.info/2010/06/05/playstation-2-controller-arduino-library-v1-0/

Github links for each
https://github.com/netlabtoolkit/VarSpeedServo
https://github.com/madsci1016/Arduino-PS2X




